data.text:
Property Description for 1616 16 Street NW

Welcome home that is located in the heart of Aster community. The open concept throughout the main floor with Den/office, 3-piece bathroom and kitchen with stainless appliances and walk-in pantry. Open to blow ceiling in living room with fireplace and overlooking staircase gives the tremendous light and openness throughout the house. Upstairs master room with his and her sink in bathroom and Walkin closet. upstairs also features the family room for your kids or family entertainment with other 2 bedroom and laundry room. The unfinished basement with SEPARATE ENTRANCE is waiting for your future development. The house is located to very close proximity to Grocery, shopping, playgrounds, schools, Meadow Rec Center and other amenities.
